{"id":102,"name":"龙血武姬","alias":"Shyvana","title":"希瓦娜","shortBio":"希瓦娜是一位迅猛的半龙人战士。她平时以人的形象出现，但也能以巨龙的身姿统治天空，用龙息烈焰焚尽敌人。作为皇子嘉文四世曾经的救命恩人，希瓦娜如今在皇子的卫队中效力。她兢兢业业，试图在多疑的德玛西亚人中求得接纳。","isVisibleInClient":true,"tacticalInfo":{"style":6,"difficulty":1,"damageType":"kMixed","attackType":"melee"},"playstyleInfo":{"damage":2,"durability":2,"crowdControl":1,"mobility":2,"utility":1},"championTagInfo":{"championTagPrimary":"","championTagSecondary":""},"squarePortraitPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-icons/102.png","stingerSfxPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-sfx-audios/102.ogg","chooseVoPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-choose-vo/102.ogg","banVoPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-ban-vo/102.ogg","roles":["fighter","tank"],"recommendedItemDefaults":[],"skins":[{"id":102000,"contentId":"0b591b96-6840-4c00-a1c6-e087550d903a","isBase":true,"name":"龙血武姬","skinClassification":"kChampion","splashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Shyvana/Skins/Base/Images/Shyvana_splash_centered_0.Shyvana_Rework.jpg","uncenteredSplashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Shyvana/Skins/Base/Images/Shyvana_splash_uncentered_0.Shyvana_Rework.jpg","tilePath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Shyvana/Skins/Base/Images/Shyvana_splash_tile_0.Shyvana_Rework.jpg","loadScreenPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Shyvana/Skins/Base/ShyvanaLoadScreen_0.Shyvana_Rework.jpg","skinType":"","rarity":"kNoRarity","isLegacy":false,"splashVideoPath":null,"previewVideoUrl":null,"collectionSplashVideoPath":null,"collectionCardHoverVideoPath":null,"featuresText":null,"chromaPath":null,"emblems":null,"regionRarityId":0,"rarityGemPath":null,"skinLines":null,"description":null},{"id":102001,"contentId":"aa1ad59a-98c1-4a28-a001-b26a64daa2de","isBase":false,"name":"钢之逆鳞 希瓦娜","skinClassification":"kChampion","splashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Shyvana/Skins/Skin01/Images/Shyvana_splash_centered_1.Shyvana_Rework.jpg","uncenteredSplashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Shyvana/Skins/Skin01/Images/Shyvana_splash_uncentered_1.Shyvana_Rework.jpg","tilePath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Shyvana/Skins/Skin01/Images/Shyvana_splash_tile_1.Shyvana_Rework.jpg","loadScreenPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Shyvana/Skins/Skin01/ShyvanaLoadScreen_1.Shyvana_Rework.jpg","skinType":"","rarity":"kNoRarity","isLegacy":false,"splashVideoPath":null,"previewVideoUrl":null,"collectionSplashVideoPath":null,"collectionCardHoverVideoPath":null,"featuresText":null,"chromaPath":null,"emblems":null,"regionRarityId":0,"rarityGemPath":null,"skinLines":[{"id":38}],"description":"希瓦娜想在《峡谷勇者》中扮演一头强大的巨龙，这很合情理。但更令她的伙伴们惊讶的是，这款游戏激发了他们这位一向严于律己的朋友身上那种令人愉悦的破坏欲。希瓦娜·钢之逆鳞兴高采烈地降临战场，一声怒吼就能将敌人和模型棋子轰飞（有时甚至连她的盟友也无法幸免）。"},{"id":102002,"contentId":"9e5e120b-c4ff-4bcd-bac4-6e120a42705b","isBase":false,"name":"骸骨之爪 希瓦娜","skinClassification":"kChampion","splashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Shyvana/Skins/Skin02/Images/Shyvana_splash_centered_2.Shyvana_Rework.jpg","uncenteredSplashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Shyvana/Skins/Skin02/Images/Shyvana_splash_uncentered_2.Shyvana_Rework.jpg","tilePath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Shyvana/Skins/Skin02/Images/Shyvana_splash_tile_2.Shyvana_Rework.jpg","loadScreenPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Shyvana/Skins/Skin02/ShyvanaLoadScreen_2.Shyvana_Rework.jpg","skinType":"","rarity":"kNoRarity","isLegacy":false,"splashVideoPath":null,"previewVideoUrl":null,"collectionSplashVideoPath":null,"collectionCardHoverVideoPath":null,"featuresText":null,"chromaPath":null,"emblems":null,"regionRarityId":0,"rarityGemPath":null,"skinLines":[{"id":32}],"description":"很多猎人声称希瓦娜在击杀那些称霸大地的巨兽时有一项得天独厚的优势。希瓦娜她自己倒不怎么在意他们的看法，宁愿将她的怒意引导至她的真正形态——一头体型巨大、喷吐炎息的巨龙……足以证明那些猎人们的观点。"},{"id":102003,"contentId":"0f9d5404-6c5e-4e65-bf55-eda6a367a69a","isBase":false,"name":"黯黑魔龙 希瓦娜","skinClassification":"kChampion","splashPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Shyvana/