on-chroma-images/102/102023.png","colors":["#27211C","#27211C"],"descriptions":[],"description":"","rarities":[]},{"id":102024,"name":"玉剑传说 舞龙卫 丁香","contentId":"12d3c731-930f-4663-adf1-d3adc4ddad4e","skinClassification":"kRecolor","chromaPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-chroma-images/102/102024.png","tilePath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-chroma-images/102/102024.png","colors":["#E58BA5","#E58BA5"],"descriptions":[],"description":"","rarities":[{"region":"TENCENT","rarity":1}]},{"id":102025,"name":"玉剑传说 舞龙卫 珠光","contentId":"503aaed1-5600-474f-92c4-056dae26c2b9","skinClassification":"kRecolor","chromaPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-chroma-images/102/102025.png","tilePath":"/lol-game-data/assets/v1/champion-chroma-images/102/102025.png","colors":["#ECF9F8","#ECF9F8"],"descriptions":[],"description":"","rarities":[]}],"emblems":null,"regionRarityId":0,"rarityGemPath":null,"skinLines":[{"id":81}],"description":"一百年来，舞龙卫本是旸刚派洞天的看守，但在救了一位落水僧人的子弟后，师父恩准她开始修炼。 她很享受化为人形所带来的种种纠葛。与星仙子不同，舞龙卫毫不怀疑自己的身份：至尊修仙学派的保护者。"}],"passive":{"name":"龙鳞铁衣","abilityIconPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Shyvana/HUD/Icons2D/Shyvana_Passive.Shyvana_Rework.png","abilityVideoPath":"champion-abilities/0102/ability_0102_P1.webm","abilityVideoImagePath":"champion-abilities/0102/ability_0102_P1.jpg","description":"参与击杀敌方英雄、大型小兵和大型野怪后，希瓦娜会获得【龙鳞铁衣】层数，从而改进她的防御属性。"},"spells":[{"spellKey":"q","name":"焚焰打击","abilityIconPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Shyvana/HUD/Icons2D/Shyvana_Q1.Shyvana_Rework.png","abilityVideoPath":"champion-abilities/0102/ability_0102_Q1.webm","abilityVideoImagePath":"champion-abilities/0102/ability_0102_Q1.jpg","cost":"无消耗","cooldown":"@Cooldown@秒 %i:cooldown%","description":"希瓦娜的下次攻击会打击目标和周围区域。这个技能可以再次施放。在【魔龙形态】下，它提供一次额外的再次施放，对单体目标造成巨额伤害。","dynamicDescription":"<spellPassive>被动：</spellPassive>希瓦娜的攻击附带<magicDamage>@Calc_Max_Health_Damage@最大生命值的魔法伤害</magicDamage><OnHit>%i:OnHit%</OnHit>并使这个技能的冷却时间缩短@Cooldown_Reduction@秒。<br><br><spellActive>主动：</spellActive>希瓦娜的下次攻击会打击目标和周围区域，造成<physicalDamage>@Calc_Damage@物理伤害</physicalDamage>。在接下来的@RecastDuration@秒内，这个技能可以在一次攻击或短暂延迟后<recast>再次施放</recast>。<br><br><keywordMajor>魔龙形态：</keywordMajor>希瓦娜获得一次额外的<recast>再次施放</recast>，使她的下次攻击噬咬目标从而造成<trueDamage>@Calc_Dragon_Form_Damage@真实伤害</trueDamage>。@SpellModifierDescriptionAppend@","range":[25000.0000,25000.0000,25000.0000,25000.0000,25000.0000,25000.0000],"costCoefficients":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"cooldownCoefficients":[10.0000,9.0000,8.0000,7.0000,6.0000,6.0000],"coefficients":{"coefficient1":0.0000,"coefficient2":0.0000},"effectAmounts":{"Effect1Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect2Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect3Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect4Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect5Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect6Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect7Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect8Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect9Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect10Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000]},"ammo":{"ammoRechargeTime":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"maxAmmo":[0,0,0,0,0,0]},"maxLevel":0},{"spellKey":"w","name":"烈火圣盾","abilityIconPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Shyvana/HUD/Icons2D/Shyvana_W1.Shyvana_Rework.png","abilityVideoPath":"champion-abilities/0102/ability_0102_W1.webm","abilityVideoImagePath":"champion-abilities/0102/ability_0102_W1.jpg","cost":"无消耗","cooldown":"@Cooldown@秒 %i:cooldown%","description":"希瓦娜获得一个护盾和移动速度，并在短暂延迟后，她周围的区域会被引爆。在【魔龙形态】下，这次爆炸如果击中一个敌方英雄，则会治疗希瓦娜。","dynamicDescription":"希瓦娜将她自身包裹在烈焰中@Duration@秒，从而获得<shield>@Calc_Shield@护盾值</shield>，附近的每个敌方英雄都会使这个护盾值提升<shield>@Calc_Shield_Per_Nearby_Champion@</shield>；此外还会获得<speed>@MoveSpeed@移动速度</speed>，这个移速加成会在朝着敌方英雄移动时提升至<speed>@MoveSpeedTowardsEnemies@</speed>。<br><br>在这些效果结束时、<shield>护盾</shield>被打破时、或在<recast>再次施放</recast>时，她附近的区域会被引爆，造成<magicDamage>@Damage@魔法伤害</magicDamage>。<br><br><keywordMajor>魔龙形态：</keywordMajor>如果这次引爆命中了一个敌方英雄，那么希瓦娜会<healing>回复@Calc_Heal_Min@到@Calc_Heal_Max@生命值</healing>，基于她的已损失生命值。@SpellModifierDescriptionAppend@","range":[350.0000,350.0000,350.0000,350.0000,350.0000,350.0000],"costCoefficients":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"cooldownCoefficients":[14.0000,13.5000,13.0000,12.5000,12.0000,12.0000],"coefficients":{"coefficient1":0.0000,"coefficient2":0.0000},"effectAmounts":{"Effect1Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect2Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect3Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect4Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect5Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect6Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect7Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect8Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect9Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect10Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000]},"ammo":{"ammoRechargeTime":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"maxAmmo":[0,0,0,0,0,0]},"maxLevel":0},{"spellKey":"e","name":"爆炎吐息","abilityIconPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Shyvana/HUD/Icons2D/Shyvana_E.Shyvana_Rework.png","abilityVideoPath":"champion-abilities/0102/ability_0102_E1.webm","abilityVideoImagePath":"champion-abilities/0102/ability_0102_E1.jpg","cost":"无消耗","cooldown":"@Cooldown@秒 %i:cooldown%","description":"希瓦娜发射一团火球，火球在击中一个大型目标时爆炸并将其减速。在【魔龙形态】下，它会穿过敌人并在击中大型目标时爆炸，还会留下一条烈焰轨迹。","dynamicDescription":"希瓦娜向目标位置投出一团火球，造成<magicDamage>@Damage@魔法伤害</magicDamage>和<status>持续@SlowDuration@秒的@Calc_Slow@减速</status>。它会在击中一个敌人或达到终点时爆炸。<br><br><keywordMajor>魔龙形态：</keywordMajor>希瓦娜的火球更大并会穿过敌人们。在击中一个英雄、大型野怪、或达到它的终点时，它会触发一道烈焰脉冲来造成<magicDamage>@Calc_Dragon_Damage@魔法伤害</magicDamage>和<status>持续@SlowDuration@秒的@Calc_Slow_Dragon@减速</status>。火球留下一条持续@GroundLingerDuration@秒的轨迹，<magicDamage>每秒造成@DamagePerSecond@魔法伤害</magicDamage>。 @SpellModifierDescriptionAppend@","range":[800.0000,800.0000,800.0000,800.0000,800.0000,800.0000],"costCoefficients":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"cooldownCoefficients":[12.0000,11.5000,11.0000,10.5000,10.0000,10.0000],"coefficients":{"coefficient1":0.0000,"coefficient2":0.0000},"effectAmounts":{"Effect1Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect2Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect3Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect4Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect5Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect6Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect7Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect8Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect9Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect10Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000]},"ammo":{"ammoRechargeTime":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"maxAmmo":[0,0,0,0,0,0]},"maxLevel":0},{"spellKey":"r","name":"魔龙降世","abilityIconPath":"/lol-game-data/assets/ASSETS/Characters/Shyvana/HUD/Icons2D/Shyvana_R.Shyvana_Rework.png","abilityVideoPath":"champion-abilities/0102/ability_0102_R1.webm","abilityVideoImagePath":"champion-abilities/0102/ability_0102_R1.jpg","cost":"需要100<keywordMajor>龙怒</keywordMajor>","cooldown":"无冷却时间","description":"希瓦娜变形成一头魔龙并向前跳跃来使途经的敌人们因恐惧而逃跑。在【魔龙形态】下，她的体型变得更大并且她的基础技能都会获得强化。","dynamicDescription":"<spellPassive>被动</spellPassive>：希瓦娜的攻击和技能在击中敌人时会生成<keywordMajor>@Fury_Generation@龙怒</keywordMajor>，在<keywordMajor>魔龙形态</keywordMajor>下的生成量会提升@TT_Fury_Mult@，并且在击中一个区域内的非英雄单位时的生成量会降低@TT_Fury_AoE_Penalty@。<br><br><spellActive>主动</spellActive>：希瓦娜变形成她的<keywordMajor>魔龙形态</keywordMajor>，期间进入<attention>不可阻挡</attention>状态，在飞向目标位置的同时对下方的敌人们喷吐火焰，对其造成<magicDamage>@Damage@魔法伤害</magicDamage>并使其<status>逃跑@FearDuration@秒</status>。<br><br>在变形状态下，希瓦娜的基础技能都会获得强化，她会获得<scaleHealth>@Calc_Bonus_Health@额外生命值</scaleHealth>、体型和攻击距离。希瓦娜持续损失<keywordMajor>龙怒</keywordMajor>并且她的变形会在她没有剩余<keywordMajor>龙怒</keywordMajor>时结束。@SpellModifierDescriptionAppend@","range":[1050.0000,1050.0000,1050.0000,1050.0000,1050.0000,1050.0000],"costCoefficients":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"cooldownCoefficients":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"coefficients":{"coefficient1":0.0000,"coefficient2":0.0000},"effectAmounts":{"Effect1Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect2Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect3Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect4Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect5Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect6Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect7Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect8Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect9Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"Effect10Amount":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000]},"ammo":{"ammoRechargeTime":[0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000,0.0000],"maxAmmo":[0,0,0,0,0,0]},"maxLevel":0}]}